{
  "id": "adv_card_hrk_04_03",
  "title": "佐伯遙子 3話 みんなの視線を釘付け",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ライブ当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Day of the live",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 2.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_03-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "結局、恥ずかしさを克服出来ないまま\nライブ当日になっちゃった……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In the end‚ I couldn't overcome my embarrassment‚\nand it's already the day of the live performance…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 8.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_03-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "こうなったら開き直るしかないわ\nステージに出たら恥ずかしいなんて言ってられないもの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "At this point‚ I have to face it head-on.\nI can't afford to feel embarrassed on stage.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_03-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "不安はあるけど、きっとなんとかなるわよね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm nervous‚ but I'll manage somehow‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.2333333351,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 15.2333333351
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 19.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（遙子さん、表情が硬いな……）\n（少しでも緊張を解してあげたいけど……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Haruko-san seems tense…)\n(I want to help her relax even a little…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば遙子さんは新衣装を着た姿を\n橋本さんに見せましたか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By the way‚ did you show the new outfit\nto Hashimoto-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_03-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "あっまだ彼女の前で着たことはないけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ I haven't worn it in front of her yet…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "今回は橋本さんが中心になって作ったじゃないですか？\nかなり苦戦したと言っていたので……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hashimoto-san was mainly involved in creating it this time‚ right?\nShe mentioned that it was quite challenging…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 42.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "きっと橋本さんも衣装の出来が気になってるはずです\n良かったら本番前に見せてあげて下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sure Hashimoto-san is curious about how the outfit turned out.\nIf it's okay‚ show it to her before the performance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 49.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_03-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "そうね……分かったわ\n着替えたらさとみちゃんに見せて感想を聞いてみるわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… I understand.\nAfter changing‚ I'll show it to Satomi-chan and ask for her opinion.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 57.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 57.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "もうすぐサニピの出番か……\n遙子さんはちゃんと着替えられたかな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's almost Sunny Peace's turn…\nI wonder if Haruko-san managed to change her clothes properly…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.4,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3199.999999999996,
          "startTime": 64.6
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 64.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_03-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "お待たせ\n着替えてきたけど……どう？　おかしくないかしら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry to keep you waiting.\nI changed my clothes… How does it look? Is it weird?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 71.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さん……よく似合ってますよ\nやっとちゃんと衣装を見せてくれましたね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haruko-san… It suits you very well.\nFinally‚ you showed me the outfit properly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_03-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "心配かけてごめんね、でももう大丈夫\n今日はこの衣装で精一杯頑張るわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sorry for worrying you‚ but I'm fine now.\nI'll do my best with this outfit today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 86.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "吹っ切れたみたいで安心しました\nもしかして橋本さんから何か言われたんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm relieved to see you looking determined.\nDid Hashimoto-san say something to you‚ by any chance?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 92.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_03-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "ええ、実は……私が衣装を着るのをためらってたせいで\nさとみちゃんはずっと不安だったらしいの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ actually… Because I hesitated to wear the outfit‚\nSatomi-chan has been worried all along.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_03-hrk009.m4a",
      "text": "私が新しい衣装を気に入らなかったんじゃないかと\n心配してたって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She was concerned that I didn't like the new outfit\nand was worried about it…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 106.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_03-hrk010.m4a",
      "text": "だから私がこの衣装を着て「ありがとう」って\nさとみちゃんに伝えたら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So when I wore this outfit and told her \"Thank you‚\"\nshe cried tears of joy and said‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_03-hrk011.m4a",
      "text": "「着てもらえて凄く嬉しいです！　私の見込んだ通り\nばっちり似合ってます！」って涙を流して喜んでくれて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"I'm really happy you wore it!\nIt suits you perfectly‚ just as I expected!\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 122.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_03-hrk012.m4a",
      "text": "それで気付いたの、さとみちゃんだけじゃない\nこの衣装には沢山の人が関わってる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's when I realized it wasn't just Satomi-chan.\nMany people were involved in this outfit…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_03-hrk013.m4a",
      "text": "この衣装はみんなが私のために心血を注いで\n作ってくれたものなんだって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This outfit was made by everyone\npouring their hearts into it for me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 137.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_03-hrk014.m4a",
      "text": "そう思ったら、恥ずかしいから着られないなんて\n口が裂けても言えないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I thought about that‚ I couldn't say I couldn't wear it\nbecause I felt embarrassed.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "衣装だけじゃありません\nメイクやスタイリスト、演出家や舞台照明さん達……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's not just the outfit.\nThe makeup‚ stylists‚ directors‚ and stage lighting staff…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 150.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さんをより魅力的にするために\n大勢の人達がベストを尽くしてくれています",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Many people are doing their best\nto make Haruko-san more attractive.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 156.7333333333
    },
    {
